article_title: Watch: SNL's Michael Che Rips Senate's Vote to Defund Planned Parenthood
article_text:
SIGN UP FOR OUR NEWSLETTER

During this week’s “Weekend Update” on NBC’s “Saturday Night Live,” Michael Che blasted the senate for voting to defund Planned Parenthood Thursday following the San Bernardino shooting.

SIGN UP FOR OUR NEWSLETTER

“Good job, dudes! There have been more mass shootings in the U.S. this year than there have been days in the year. So, how is defunding Planned Parenthood the priority right now? It would be like if you called the exterminator and he goes, ‘Whoa, you’ve got a lot of rats in here, man. So, the first thing we’ve gotta do is defund Planned Parenthood.'”

Follow Trent Baker on Twitter @MagnifiTrent.
